{"tid":1957550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"HK01: 第4名中招警員  曾參與「人群管理行動」","createTime":"2020-04-04T04:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T15:14:20.000Z","uid":227801,"like":569,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa738f66b7046f1460fbfe088439c6460c02f49","tid":1957550,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"【11:59】警方發言人表示，一名駐守西九龍總區46歲男警長初步確診2019冠狀病毒病。該名警長隸屬機動部隊，過去14日曾參與反罪惡巡邏及人群管理行動，沒有外遊記錄，亦非早前確診警員的緊密接觸者。他在4月2日感到不適，到政府醫院求醫，經初步測試後於昨日（4月3日）晚上得知對2019冠狀病毒病呈陽性反應。連同此個案，目前有4名警員感染新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔通係331 鎮壓</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7daca0c8f671c20522421244ce148ced7aa230fd","tid":1957550,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f102e0a265e105269967731017e6114bc67e1e6","tid":1957550,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8184cd8d977bd052655d8309e2c3a4945aa7fc83","tid":1957550,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a057dcf0c4a1d3db11f590c0bf81eb032df06e","tid":1957550,"uid":235152,"like":36,"dislike":10,"score":26,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:14:44.000Z","msg":"手足播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2801700714684e557bd615c996c4385726ed697","tid":1957550,"uid":189328,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"46歲都算高危<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29292b0f0e996fcf8b0cf23595f15f2558